Package ACRUSalinity.Data

Class Summary
DAbstractionSaltLoad This class is used to store daily TDS concentration of abstracted water from a reservoir.
DActualIrrigApplic This class stores the depth of irrigation water applied to the field excluding all irrigation losses.
DActualQuickflowDepth This class is currently getting its data from ACRU.Processes.Psurfaceflow.PSCSRunoff
DAppliedFertilizer This class stores the monthly quantity of fertilizer and gypsum applied to the field.
DBaseflowSalinity This class stores the daily baseflow salinity from irrigated and non-irrigated areas.
DBaseflowSaltLoad This class stores the daily salt load associated with baseflow release.
DDelayedStormFlowWaterFluxRecord This class stores and conducts internal computation related with delayed stormflow salt load in association with its parent classes.
DFertilizerFluxRecord Stores and performs an internal salt balance computations on the total fertilizer and gypsum applied to a particular land NB. this data object is for use only with the process under development to account the impact of fertilizer and gypsum applicaton on surface TDS balance.
DFertilizerReleaseCoeff Stores the fertilizer release coefficient.
DGeneratedSaltLoad Stores the salt load generated from topsoil, subsoil and groundwater store both in irrigated and non-irrigated areas.
DGroundwaterSalinity This class stores the daily groundwater salinity.
DImperviousAreaSaltLoad Stores the salt load associated with runoff water from adjunct and disjunct impervious areas.
DInflowSaltLoad Stores the total salt load associated with total inflows (including rainfall) to a reservoir.
DInitialSalinity Stores the TDS concentration of soil horizons and a reservoir at the start of a simulation.
DInitialSaltLoad Stores the salt load associated with the water stored in soil horizons and a reservoir at the start of a simulation.
DIrrigationWaterSalinity Stores the monthly average irrigation water salinity.
DIrrigationWaterSaltLoad Stores the daily irrigation water salt load.
DNormalflowSalinity Stores the TDS concentration of the legal (normal) flow release.
DNormalflowSaltLoad Stores the salt load associated with the normal (legal) flow release.
DOutflowSalinity This class is used to store daily river and reservoir outflow salinity data objects.
DOutflowSaltLoad Stores the daily salt load associated with the water outflowing from a reservoir or a river.
DPercSaltConc This class is used to store daily salt concentration of percolation water from A and B horizons.
DPercSaltLoad Stores the daily salt load associated with the percolation water from the soil horizons.
DPlantFerilizerUptakeCoeff Stores the coefficient of fertilizer uptake by plants.
DQuickflowSalinity Stores the daily TDS concentration of quickflow both from irrigated and non-irrigated lands.
DQuickflowSaltLoad Stores the salt load associated with the quickflow both from irrigated and non-irrigated lands.
DRainfallSalinity Stores the average TDS concentration of a rain falling over an area.
DRainfallSaltLoad This class holds the daily salt load associated with the rain falling over an area.
DReservoirEvapVol this class stores data of reservoir evaporation volume for use in hydrosalinity as determined and set in PDamSimpleEvap
DReservoirSalinity This class stores the daily TDS concentration of a reservoir's current storage.
DReservoirSalinityOption Stores the yes (1) or no (0) option as to whether the algorithms conducting reservoir TDS balance and salt routing are to be invoked in a particular simulation.
DResInflowSalinity Stores the daily average TDS concentration of water inflowing to a reservoir.
DResWaterInflow Stores the daily volume of water inflowing into a reservoir system.
DRunoffSalinity Stores the TDS concentration of runoff water both from irrigated and non-irrigated lands.
DRunoffSaltLoad Stores the salt load associated with runoff water both from irrigated and non-irrigated lands.
DSalinityOption Stores a yes (1) or no (0) option as to whether ACRUSalinity is to be executed in a particular simulation.
DSaltFluxRecord Stores and conductes internal salt balance computations with the help of its parent classes.
DSaltInput Stores the daily total salt load associated with rainfall and irrigation water added to the topsoil in a particular land.
DSaltSat stores the saturation level of topsoil, subsoil and the groundwater store both in irrigated and non-irrigated areas.
DSatUpwardFlow Stores the daily quantity of water moving upward from an underlying layer both in irrigated and non-irrigated lands.
DSeepageSalinity Stores the daily TDS concentration of seepage water from a reservoir.
DSeepageSaltLoad Stores the daily salt load associated with seepage water from reservoirs.
DSpillwayflowSalinity Stores the daily TDS concentration of water flowing out of a reservoir through the spillway.
DSpillwayflowSaltLoad Stores the salt load associated with the daily flow of water out of a reservoir through the spillway.
DStormflowSalinity Stores the daily TDS concentration of stormflow both in irrigated and non-irrigated lands.
DStormflowStoreSalinity Stores the salt load associated with the stormflow both in irrigated and non-irrigated lands.
DStormflowStoreSaltLoad This class is used to store daily salt load associated with the delayed stormflow store.
DSubsoilSalinity The daily TDS concentration of subsoil water.
DSurfaceSaltFluxRecord This class stores and conducts internal surface salt balance computations in association with its parent classes.
DTopsoilSalinity Stores the daily TDS concentration in topsoil horizon.
DUptakeRateConstant This class stores the value of the salt uptake rate parameter for the topsoil, subsoil and groundwater store of both irrigated and non-irrigated lands.
DUpwardSaltFlux Stores the daily salt load associated with upward moving water from underlying layer.
DWaterOutflow This class stores a daily outflow volume of water (in litres) from a particular river or channel reach.
